cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the development of a deep learning platform specifically for medical image analysis, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The platform also includes features such as data augmentation and evaluation metrics, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the use of deep learning networks for medical image analysis involves optimization and training, which falls under the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
